@startuml
title 行情工作流 - 时间驱动图
participant "时钟 / 市场时间" as Clock
participant "MarketWorkflow" as Workflow

== 盘中周期 ==
Clock -> Workflow : bar 到达
Workflow -> Workflow : on_bars 主链

== 指定时刻 ==
Clock -> Workflow : 14:50
Workflow -> Workflow : 换月检查

== 保存周期 ==
Clock -> Workflow : autosave 周期到达
Workflow -> Workflow : maybe_save

== 订阅刷新周期 ==
Clock -> Workflow : subscription_refresh_sec 到达
Workflow -> Workflow : reconcile_subscriptions(timer)
@enduml
